{"id":2000,"date":"2020-08-24T19:44:18","date_gmt":"2020-08-24T12:44:18","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/?page_id=2000"},"modified":"2020-09-13T20:58:05","modified_gmt":"2020-09-13T13:58:05","slug":"concierge-vi","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/concierge-vi\/","title":{"rendered":"Concierge"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"ffb-id-47lnta7c fg-image  img-responsive full-width fg-text-dark\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/exp.jpg 1992w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/80f86359ba6cc27f702acbafc79ab208_exp-320-c-100.jpg 320w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/80f86359ba6cc27f702acbafc79ab208_exp-768-c-100.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/80f86359ba6cc27f702acbafc79ab208_exp-992-c-100.jpg 992w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/80f86359ba6cc27f702acbafc79ab208_exp-1200-c-100.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1992px) 100vw, 1992px\" src=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/exp.jpg\" alt=\"Our Concierge team are available and ready to assist you with your needs and provide local expertise and knowledge to ensure your time in Ho Chi Minh City is enjoyable and fulfilling.\"><style><\/style><script type=\"text\/javascript\"><\/script><section class=\"ffb-id-48j07qu4 fg-section fg-text-dark\"><div class=\"fg-container container-fluid fg-container-fluid fg-container-lvl--1 \"><div class=\"fg-row row fg-row-no-gutter   \" ><div class=\"ffb-id-48j07qu5 fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-12 fg-text-dark\"><h1 class=\"ffb-id-48j07qu8 fg-heading text-center    fg-text-dark\">D\u1ecaCH V\u1ee4 CONCIERGE<\/h1><div class=\"ffb-id-48j07qu9 fg-paragraph ff-richtext text-left    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">N\u1eb1m \u1edf s\u1ea3nh ch&iacute;nh c\u1ee7a kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n, \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 Concierge lu&ocirc;n s\u1eb5n s&agrave;ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 y&ecirc;u c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch v&agrave; chia s\u1ebb nh\u1eefng th&ocirc;ng tin du l\u1ecbch b\u1ed5 &iacute;ch, mang \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian \u0111&aacute;ng nh\u1edb cho du kh&aacute;ch khi \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi th&agrave;nh ph\u1ed1 H\u1ed3 Ch&iacute; Minh.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch c&oacute; th\u1ec3 tham kh\u1ea3o c&aacute;c th&ocirc;ng tin v\u1ec1 c&aacute;c tour \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c du kh&aacute;ch y&ecirc;u th&iacute;ch \u1edf b&ecirc;n d\u01b0\u1edbi. Ngo\u1ea3i ra, \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 Concierge c\u1ee7a ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i s\u1ebd s\u1eb5n s&agrave;ng \u0111\u1ec3 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr&igrave;nh ri&ecirc;ng ph&ugrave; h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi l\u1ecbch tr&igrave;nh v&agrave; mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a m\u1ed7i Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Vui l&ograve;ng li&ecirc;n h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Tr\u01b0\u1edfng b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn qua email: <a href=\"mailto:tung.nguyen@caravellehotel.com\">tung.nguyen@caravellehotel.com<\/a> tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eddi gian l\u01b0u tr&uacute; \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 l&ecirc;n k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch v&agrave; s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp th\u1eddi gian.&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">M\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m th&uacute; v\u1ecb nh\u1ecf: Tr\u01b0\u1edfng B\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn Concierge, Mr. Tung Nguyen \u0111&atilde; t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p m\u1ed9t danh s&aacute;ch &ldquo;C&aacute;c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0103n u\u1ed1ng v&agrave; gi\u1ea3i tr&iacute; t\u1ea1i S&agrave;i G&ograve;n&rdquo; v&ocirc; c&ugrave;ng \u0111\u1eb7c s\u1eafc, l&agrave; m\u1ed9t danh s&aacute;ch m&agrave; b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 du kh&aacute;ch y&ecirc;u \u1ea9m th\u1ef1c v&agrave; v\u0103n h&oacute;a S&agrave;i G&ograve;n kh&oacute; c&oacute; th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua.<\/p>\n<p><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/section><style>.ffb-id-48j07qu4{ padding-to