 Vietnam\"><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-48j0c8d5 fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-12 fg-text-dark\"><h1 class=\"ffb-id-48j0c8d8 fg-heading text-center    fg-text-dark\">C\u00c1C TOUR DU L\u1ecaCH H\u1ea4P D\u1eaaN<\/h1><div class=\"ffb-id-48j0c8d9 fg-paragraph ff-richtext text-left    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Sunset Cruise &ndash; Ng\u1eafm ho&agrave;ng h&ocirc;n tr&ecirc;n s&ocirc;ng:<\/strong> Kh&aacute;m ph&aacute; h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng k&ecirc;nh v&agrave; s&ocirc;ng xung quanh S&agrave;i G&ograve;n c&ugrave;ng nh\u1eefng n&eacute;t \u0111\u1eb9p \u0111\u1eddi th\u01b0\u1eddng d\u1ecdc theo \u0111&ocirc;i b\u1edd. T\u1ea1m r\u1eddi xa kh\u1ecfi khu n\u1ed9i \u0111&ocirc; t\u1ea5p n\u1eadp v&agrave; xu&ocirc;i theo nh\u1eefng con k&ecirc;nh r\u1ee3p b&oacute;ng c&acirc;y, \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ecba danh m&agrave; ng\u01b0\u1eddi d&acirc;n \u1edf \u0111&oacute; v\u1eabn s\u1ed1ng ch&acirc;n ph\u01b0\u01a1ng v&agrave; g&igrave;n gi\u1eef nhi\u1ec1u gi&aacute; tr\u1ecb truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng qu&yacute; gi&aacute;. T\u1ea1m bi\u1ec7t chuy\u1ebfn du l\u1ecbch k&eacute;o d&agrave;i 2 gi\u1edd n&agrave;y v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u1eefa \u0103n nh\u1eb9 v&agrave; khung c\u1ea3nh ho&agrave;ng h&ocirc;n r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1. \u0110\u0103ng k&yacute; theo c&aacute; nh&acirc;n ho\u1eb7c chung v\u1edbi nh&oacute;m.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">_____________<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Vespa City Tour &ndash; C\u01b0\u1ee1i xe Vespa, kh&aacute;m ph&aacute; th&agrave;nh ph\u1ed1:<\/strong> C&ugrave;ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i xe c\u1ee7a Vespa Tour tham gia v&agrave;o m\u1ed9t tour th&agrave;nh ph\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111&aacute;o \u0111\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u r&otilde; h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t S&agrave;i G&ograve;n gi&agrave;u m&agrave;u l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, v\u0103n h&oacute;a v&agrave; ... s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng xe m&aacute;y tham gia giao th&ocirc;ng. Tour s\u1ebd bao g\u1ed3m 2 gi\u1edd d\u1ea1o quanh c&aacute;c Qu\u1eadn trung t&acirc;m v&agrave; khu v\u1ef1c v\u1eabn c&ograve;n gi\u1eef nhi\u1ec1u \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a ki\u1ebfn tr&uacute;c \u0110&ocirc;ng D\u01b0\u01a1ng. B\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u v&agrave;o khung gi\u1edd chi\u1ec1u, du kh&aacute;ch khi tham gia chuy\u1ebfn \u0111i s\u1ebd c&oacute; d\u1ecbp ng\u1ed3i sau y&ecirc;n xe scooter c\u1ed5 \u0111i\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc &Yacute;, d\u1ea1o quanh nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ecba danh l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v&agrave; s&ocirc;ng S&agrave;i G&ograve;n v&agrave; ng\u1eafm nh&igrave;n cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi d&acirc;n S&agrave;i G&ograve;n.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">_____________<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Du l\u1ecbch v\u1ec1 mi\u1ec1n s&ocirc;ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Nam B\u1ed9:<\/strong> \u0110\u1ed3ng b\u1eb1ng s&ocirc;ng C\u1eedu Long, v\u1ef1a l&uacute;a tr&ugrave; ph&uacute; nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam.&nbsp; D&ugrave; ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn khu v\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u1eb1ng v\u1eabn c&ograve;n c&oacute; v\u1ebb hoang s\u01a1, \u0111&acirc;y l\u1ea1i l&agrave; m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng khu v\u1ef1c c&oacute; m\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed9 d&acirc;n s\u1ed1 cao nh\u1ea5t Vi\u1ec7t Nam v&agrave; m\u1ed7i t\u1ea5c \u0111\u1ea5t \u1edf \u0111&acirc;y \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 ph&aacute;t tri\u1ec3n n&ocirc;ng nghi\u1ec7p! Theo tour v\u1ec1 \u0111&acirc;y, du kh&aacute;ch s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ea7y th\u01b0 th&aacute;i \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb quang c\u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3ng l&uacute;a b&aacute;t ng&aacute;t, nh\u1eefng b&egrave; c&aacute; s&ocirc;i n\u1ed5i hay nh\u1eefng h&agrave;ng c&acirc;y s\u0103n tr&aacute;i n\u1ed1i \u0111u&ocirc;i nhau.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">_____________<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>\u0110\u1ecba \u0111\u1ea1o C\u1ee7 Chi:<\/strong> M\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m du l\u1ecbch \u0111&atilde; r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed7i quen thu\u1ed9c nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t chuy\u1ebfn \u0111i v\u1ec1 th\u0103m l\u1ea1i khu v\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ecba \u0111\u1ea1o d&agrave;i h\u01a1n 200 km n&agrave;y lu&ocirc;n l&agrave;m du kh&aacute;ch c&oacute; nh\u1eefng c\u1ea3m x&uacute;c b\u1ed3i h\u1ed3i. L&agrave; m\u1ed9t di t&iacute;ch l\u1ecbch s\u1eed huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i g\u1eafn li\u1ec1n v\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn v\u1ec7 qu\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam, \u0111\u1ecba \u0111\u1ea1o C\u1ee7 Chi d\u1eabn du kh&aacute;ch lu\u1ed3n l&aacute;ch qua m\u1ed9t m&ecirc; cung \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ea7m d\u01b0\u1edbi l&ograve;ng \u0111\u1ea5t v&agrave; nh\u1eefng c&aacute;nh c\u1eeda b&iacute; m\u1eadt d\u1eabn l&ecirc;n m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea5t v&ocirc; c&ugrave;ng th&uacute; v\u1ecb.<\/p>\n<p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-48j0c8da fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-6 fg-text-dark\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"ffb-id-48j0c8dc fg-image  img-responsive full-width fg-text-dark\" src=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Popular-Touring-Options-2.jpg\" alt=\"Caravelle offers a cross-section of Saigon\u2019s colourful history and its legendary motorcycle traffic: a two-hour Vespa City Tour around the main district and French-influenced quarters of Ho Chi Minh City.\"><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-48j0c8dd fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-6 fg-text-dark\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"ffb-id-48j0c8df fg-image  img-responsive full-width fg-text-dark\" src=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Popular-Touring-Options-4.jpg\" alt=\"Popular-Touring-Options-4\"><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/section><style>.ffb-id-48j07qu4{ \npadding-top: 50px;\npadding-right: 50px;\npadding-bottom: 50px;\npadding-left: 50px;\n\n}\n .ffb-id-48j07qu5{ \ntext-align: center;\n}\n.ffb-id-48j07qu9{ \npadding-bottom: 10px;\n\n}\n@media (min-width:768px) { \n.ffb-id-48j07qu9{ \npadding-bottom: 10px;\n\n}\n}@media (min-width:992px) { \n.ffb-id-48j07qu9{ \npadding-bottom: 15px;\n\n}\n}@media (min-width:1200px) { \n.ffb-id-48j07qu